OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1780063874
OL,3,CSummer inter-island ferry services
OL,4,Ccancelled
OL,6,FJersey's ferry provider, DFDS, has
OL,7,Fannounced they will suspend all
OL,8,Fplanned summer sailings between Jersey
OL,9,Fand Guernsey.
OL,11,FIt follows a decision by Guernsey's
OL,12,FCommittee for Economic Development to
OL,13,Freject the company's proposals for a
OL,14,Fweekend service between the two
OL,15,Fislands - due to "operational and
OL,16,Fresourcing challenges".
OL,18,FDFDS has now cancelled all of its
OL,19,Fplanned inter-island sailings and
OL,20,Fremoved the route from sale.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
