OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1780063874
OL,3,CSummer inter-island ferry services
OL,4,Ccancelled
OL,6,FIn a statement sent to ITV News, DFDS
OL,7,Fsaid they "remain open to further
OL,8,Fdiscussions regarding future inter-
OL,9,Fisland connectivity and continue to
OL,10,Fbelieve there is value in improving
OL,11,Flinks between the islands."
OL,13,FThe company added it would "welcome
OL,14,Ffurther engagement involving both
OL,15,Fisland governments, ports, and other
OL,16,Frelevant officials."
OL,18,FAffected customers have been sent a
OL,19,Ftext message detailing the
OL,20,Fcancellation, and will automatically
OL,21,Fbe issued a full refund.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
