OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1780063874
OL,3,CSummer inter-island ferry services
OL,4,Ccancelled
OL,6,FHaving freed up the capacity of their
OL,7,Ffleet, DFDS say they will now add
OL,8,Ffurther sailings between Jersey and St
OL,9,FMalo, to allow for summer day trips.
OL,11,FThey say this decision "supports
OL,12,Fsummer travel demand and provides
OL,13,Fadditional options for passengers".
OL,15,FThe additional sailings will run on
OL,16,Fthe dates previously earmarked for
OL,17,Finter-island services - 6th and 20th
OL,18,FJuly, alongside 3rd, 17th, and 24th
OL,19,FAugust.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
