PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1780063874
OL,3,CSummer inter-island ferry services
OL,4,Ccancelled
OL,6,FDFDS will also add an extra sailing on
OL,7,F2 July, to allow more islanders to
OL,8,Ftravel to the Le Mans motorsport event.
OL,10,FWhen the States of Jersey signed a 20-
OL,11,Fyear contract with the ferry provider,
OL,12,Fthey promised to deliver a reciprocal
OL,13,Finter-island service once a week.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
